Package projectElectus

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Locatable
    This class creates the interface implemented by Platform.java and used by its subclasses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Character
    This class creates and manages the player's character.
    Credits
    This class creates the Credits frame when it is created as an object.
    Enemy
    This class creates and manages the enemies in the game.
    Entity
    This class creates and manages any entities in the game.
    ErrorLog
    This class creates and writes to an Error Log when an error is encountered.
    Explosion  
    Game
    This class creates and manages the game itself.
    GameOver
    This class creates the Game Over frame when it is created as an object when the Character runs out of health.
    GameRunner
    This class creates the game frame and canvas for the game.
    Instructions
    This class creates the Instructions frame when it is created as an object.
    Main
    The main class, which initiates the game and shows the Title Screen.
    Menu
    This class creates the Menu frame when it is created as an object.
    Platform
    This class creates and manages any Platforms in the game.
    Projectile
    This class creates and manages any Projectiles in the game.
    TitleScreen
    This class creates the Title Screen frame when it is created as an object.
